@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### V1 - list events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events

### V1 - get event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events/1

### V2 - list events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/events

### V2 - get event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/events/1

### Inspect V1 deprecation headers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/events
Accept: application/json

### OpenAPI document for V1
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

### OpenAPI document for V2
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v2.json
